----------------------------------------------
         A USERS GUIDE FOR SCALE-LES
       by Team SCALE UGC working group
----------------------------------------------

* make a PDF file
 >$ sh usersguide_make.sh

 then you will get a pdf file "scale_users_guide"
 in the current directory.

* texlive (more than 2009) is needed to  make
  the PDF file.

* to make PDF file complitely, "wallpaper.sty" is
  needed. it can be download freely from
  http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/macros/latex/contrib/wallpaper

----------------------------------------------
(last update: 9 July, 2015)
